    public static class QueryProviderBase.Defaults
extends Object
implements CreateRootCondition, MapRootRuleCondition, ReductionRuleCondition, PatternRuleQuery, DropRuleCondition, WeaveRuleCondition, WeaveRuleQuery, ScriptCodeBlock, MapConfigurationCondition, SourceNodeQuery, SourceNodesQuery, WeaveAnchorQuery, DropAttributeRuleCondition
    Reasonable default values for all conditions and queries. Note, these default values represent the case when no condition/query was specified. There might be another set of defaults for cases when condition failed to evaluate.
